确保下面软件已安装
  Git
  Go
  Pip
  Xcode
  Docker
  Docker Compose

安装必要工具
  brew install gnu-tar --with-default-names
  brew install libtool
  pip install --upgrade pip

下载代码必须放到$GOPATH下
  /Users/username/go/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric
  /Users/username/go/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric-samples
